    "comment_data": [
        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "lspconfig is a collection of configs. We are not going to add more and more features to it. It's just a collection of configs.\r\n\r\nNvim has `vim.lsp.start()`, you can call that and customize it endlessly. There doesn't need to be special options for every random thing.",
